{{For|other entities called "Central Okrug" or "Tsentralny Okrug"|Tsentralny Okrug (disambiguation)}} {{Infobox settlement |name=Central Administrative Okrug |native_name=Центра́льный администрати́вный о́круг |native_name_lang=ru |type=[[Administrative okrugs of Moscow|Administrative okrug]] of Moscow |image_skyline= |image_alt= |image_caption= |image_map={{#invoke:Wikidata|getImages|P242|FETCH_WIKIDATA||{{{mapsize|300px}}} }} |map_caption=Central Administrative Okrug in Moscow |coordinates = {{Coord|55|45|N|37|37|E|source:kolossus-ruwiki|display=inline,title}} |image_flag=Flag of Central district (Moscow).png |flag_link= |image_shield=CAO district of Moscow coa.png |shield_link= |subdivision_type=Country |subdivision_name=[[Russia]] |subdivision_type1=[[Federal cities of Russia|Federal city]] |subdivision_name1=[[Moscow]] |parts_type=Districts |parts=10 + [[Kitai-gorod]] |area_total_km2= |area_footnotes= |population_total= |population_as_of= |population_footnotes= |population_est |pop_est_as_of |pop_est_footnotes |established_title |established_date= |leader_title=Prefect{{citation needed|date=March 2015}} |leader_name= |website={{#property:P856|}} |date= }} '''Central Administrative Okrug''', or '''Tsentralny Administrativny Okrug''' ({{lang-ru|Центра́льный администрати́вный о́круг}}, ''Tsentralny administrativny okrug''), is one of the [[administrative divisions of Moscow|twelve]] administrative [[okrug]]s of [[Moscow]], [[Russia]], located within the [[Kamer-Kollezhny Bank]]. Population: {{ru-census2010|741,967|;}} {{ru-census2002|701,353|.}}
It was established in 1991. OKATO number 45 286 000 000.
==Territorial organisation== [[File:Moscow Central Okrug districts.png|thumb|Map of territorial entities in the okrug]] The okrug, governed by the prefecture, encompasses ten districts. The territory of [[Kitai-gorod]] is not a part of any district and is governed by the administrative okrug directly.
